                    <div class="collapsible-region collapse" id=
                    "collapsible-region-1">
                      <div>
                        
                        <p id="desc">
                          “IT IS NOT ALL OVER. EVERYTHING HAS NOT BEEN
                          INVENTED. THE WORLD IS JUST BEGINNING” – GENE
                          RODDENBERRY<br>
                          The planet is all yours and come up with a spark of
                          innovation to improve the lives around you. The stage
                          has been set to listen to your words. Hope you
                          fulfill the expectation in the form of PAPER
                          PRESENTATION.
                        </p>
                        <p></p>
                        <p id="rules">
                          Rules
                        </p>1. Interested candidates are advised to mail the
                        complete paper in IEEE format by 18th September 2015 to
                        me.bodhi2015@vjcet.org with in the subject field of the
                        e-mail.<br>
                        2. The front page should have title of paper on the top
                        and the details of the candidate including Name,
                        Semester, College, Contact number and email-ID at the
                        bottom. The number of pages of the paper should be
                        limited to a maximum of five excluding the front
                        page.<br>
                        3. The competition is open to all B. Tech students. The
                        paper should be related to Mechanical Engineering.<br>
                        4. The participants of shortlisted candidates will be
                        informed by E-mail by 19th September 2015 and they
                        would have to send reply on or before 21st September
                        2015 confirming their participation.<br>
                        5. All the candidates will get participation
                        certificates.<br>
                        6. The participants will have to present their papers
                        in MS-Power Point format only.
                        <p></p>
                        <p></p>
                        <p>
                          View paper format <a href="paper-format.pdf" target=
                          "_blank">Download</a>
                        </p>
                        <p id="coordinators">
                          Coordinators
                        </p>STUDENT CO-ORDINATORS<br>
                        Santo Dominic (9496821046)<br>
                        H. Krishnan (9645963286)<br>
