                          enough of himself and his contribution to praise the
                          skill of the others”. - NORMAN S HIDLE<br>
                          To test the logical, statistical and analyzing basic
                          engineering skills of a team. It provides a unique
                          opportunity to encounter the engineering ideas to
                          good effect.
                        </p>
                        <p></p>
                        <p id="rules">
                          Rules
                        </p>RULES<br>
                        • This event will test the logical, analytical and
                        basic engineering skills to solve a given task.<br>
                        • A maximum of 3 members per team will be allowed.<br>
                        • Prizes will be Rs.3000, Rs.2000 for 1st and 2nd
                        respectively.<br>
                        • Calculators, measuring aids etc. will not be
                        allowed.<br>
                        • Decision of judges will be final.
