                        <p id="desc">
                          “Manufacturing is more than just putting parts
                          together. It's coming up with ideas, testing
                          principles and perfecting the engineering, as well as
                          final assembly"- JAMES DYSON<br>
                          The parts of a machine will be given disassembled. It
                          has to be assembled to make the required machine. The
                          team with best time below the time limit will be
                          awarded as winner.
                        </p>
                        <p></p>
                        <p id="rules">
                          Rules
                        </p>• This event will test the technical and practical
                        skills of the contestants.<br>
                        • Competition will have various rounds and contestants
                        will be eliminated based on time.<br>
                        • Prizes will be Rs.3000, Rs.2000 for 1st and 2nd
                        respectively.<br>
                        • A team of minimum 3 members, but not exceeding 5
                        members are required.<br>
                        • Tools will be provided. Tools from outside will not
                        be permitted.<br>
                        • Time limit will be informed before the start of the
                        event<br>
                        • The teams which complete the required assembly taking
                        minimum time (within the given time limit) will secure
                        the 1st and 2nd positions resp.<br>
                        • Teams are required to register before the scheduled
                        start of the event. No registrations will be allowed
                        after the start of the event.<br>
                        • Decision of judges will be final.
                        <p></p>
                        <p></p>
                        <p id="otherdetails">
                          Other Details
                        </p>DATE & TIME: 10.00 AM – 03.00 PM, 23/09/2015<br>
                        VENUE : ENTRANCE - MECHANICAL WORKSHOP
